overview.en: AINT is to distribute data, software, operating platform resources and other digital assets to the block chain, and use the de-centralized data asset trading platform to provide information dissemination channels and promote the exchange of resources, forming an AI application trading and product customization portfolio platform.
overview.zh: AINT 是将数据、软件、运行平台资源等以数字化的资产发布到区块 链上，利用去中心化的数据资产交易平台提供信息发布渠道和促进资 源互通流转，形成一个 AI 应用交易和产品定制组合平台。
